# ApplePicker Game

Welcome to **ApplePicker**, a fun and engaging game where you catch apples in a basket while avoiding deadly poison apples! The game progressively gets harder, challenging your reflexes and decision-making skills.

## ğŸ® How to Play
- Move the basket left and right to **catch falling apples**.
- **Golden apples** give bonus points.
- **Poison apples** should be avoided â€“ catching them will **remove a life**.
- The game ends when all baskets (lives) are lost.
- Try to set the **highest score** possible!

## ğŸ›  Unique Features
âœ… **Golden Apples** â€“ Rare golden apples worth **300 points** instead of the usual 100.
âœ… **Poison Apples** â€“ Catching these will **remove a basket**, but missing them does **no penalty**.
âœ… **Game Over Screen** â€“ Displays the final score and high score, allowing you to restart.
âœ… **Start Menu** â€“ A dedicated start screen with a clean UI before the game begins.
âœ… **Increasing Difficulty** â€“ Apples fall faster as the game progresses, making it more challenging.
âœ… **Smooth Controls** â€“ Easy-to-use controls for a seamless gaming experience.
âœ… **Non-Fullscreen Window** â€“ Runs in windowed mode for easy quitting (no forced fullscreen).

## ğŸ”¥ Play the Game
### **Download the Executable**
You can download the **ApplePickerGame.exe** file from the [GitHub Releases section](https://github.com/DariusDahl/Game-Development-Project-Sync/releases) or directly from the `Builds/` folder in this repository.

**To play:**
1. Download `ApplePickerGame.exe`
2. Double-click to run
3. Enjoy!

